This is an awful (http://wiki.call-cc.org/egg/awful) application to
help making web surveys.

Surveys are specified in SXML. awful-survey provides some handy
procedures that generate SXML code for common survey widgets.

To see it in action, run the example application:

    $ cd awful-survey
    $ chicken-install
    $ awful awful-survey-app.scm

Then request http://localhost:8080 on your browser
